OL,3,CRecruitment freeze announced at
OL,4,CCornwall hospitals amid #3.5m deficit
OL,6,FThe Royal Cornwall Hospitals Trust
OL,7,F(RCHT) has announced a recruitment
OL,8,Ffreeze as it faces a #3.5m budget
OL,9,Fdeficit.
OL,11,FIt will affect Royal Cornwall Hospital
OL,12,Fat Treliske, near Truro, St Michael's
OL,13,FHospital in Hayle, and West Cornwall
OL,14,FHospital in Penzance.
OL,16,FA spokesperson for the trust said: "As
OL,17,Fwe take steps to ensure we live within
OL,18,Fthe funding available to us, we have
OL,19,Fintroduced a temporary pause on new
OL,20,Frecruitment for the next three months.
