OL,6,F"There will be exceptions, as safe
OL,7,Fcare and continuing the progress we
OL,8,Fare making in reducing waiting times
OL,9,Fwill always remain our priority.
OL,11,F"Staffing accounts for around 60 per
OL,12,Fcent of our expenditure and the
OL,13,Frecruitment pause is one of many
OL,14,Ffinancial recovery actions, as we
OL,15,Fexplore all opportunities to deliver
OL,16,Fservices more efficiently."
OL,18,FThe trust currently employs about
OL,19,F6,700 staff.
