OL,3,CRecruitment freeze announced at
OL,4,CCornwall hospitals amid #3.5m deficit
OL,6,FIt has a total budget of approximately
OL,7,F#580 million for the provision of
OL,8,Fservices at the three main sites with
OL,9,Fapproximately 750 inpatient beds.
OL,11,FA financial report presented to the
OL,12,FRCHT board meeting showed that the
OL,13,Foverall financial position in July saw
OL,14,Fa total expenditure of #225.9m against
OL,15,Fa total income of #221.8m alongside a
OL,16,F#0.6m budget, leaving a #3.5m deficit.
OL,18,FIt revealed that as well as pay
OL,19,Fexpenditure being #3.44m above plan,
OL,20,Fnon-pay expenditure is #2.67m above
OL,21,Fwhat was budgeted.
