OL,6,F"At the end of July, there was an
OL,7,Foverspend against financial plan of
OL,8,F#3.48m. The key components driving the
OL,9,Foverspend is a shortfall in the
OL,10,Fdelivery of CIP, manifesting in our
OL,11,Fpay expenditure run rate being too
OL,12,Fhigh and the cost of industrial action.
OL,14,F"Despite submitting a break-even plan,
OL,15,Fif the trust reports a material
OL,16,Fvariance to this in year, there is a
OL,17,Frisk of intervention and regulatory
OL,18,Faction from both the Integrated Care
OL,19,FBoard and NHS England.
